Recently, after a year of reading bad news online, I reached the end of my rope. I needed hope. Iâ€™d like to share with you how I restored mine.</p>

<p>To rationally find hope, one must first know how things actually stand.* So first, the bad news:</p>

<p>We, the peasantry of the world, are:</p>

<ol>
