<p>Thus, the nobility has decided to eliminate us. And not just the Jews, gays, convicts, dissidents, dark people, etc. But all 6.5 billion of us.</p>

<p>How will they accomplish this? By the following sequence of actions:</p>

<ol>
  <li>withholding energy supplies</li>
